messages.message: I'm not a good source of best practice re: test sets, but I do have this bit of information that might be useful: we've got an AWS bucket for datasets that we could use as a source of record outside of Github
Some folks also prefer `git-lfs` for this sort of thing, but we haven't explored it at IB yet
`git-lfs` is something that we may want to investigate at some point. Large binaries in vanilla git is not as awesome as one might hope. :smile:
